must check this file before implementing parser http://download.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/reflect/class/classMembers.html
good resource on sun CodeModel http://namanmehta.blogspot.com/2010/01/use-codemodel-to-generate-java-source.html


Example
JCodeModel cm = new JCodeModel();
JDefinedClass dc = cm._class("foo.Bar");
JMethod m = dc.method(0, int.class, "foo");
m.body()._return(JExpr.lit(5));

File file = new File("./target/classes");
file.mkdirs();
cm.build(file);

